## Why This Is Asked

This question assesses practical understanding of timer-driven thread wakeups, race condition handling, and efficient data structures in a kernel-like environment. It tests a candidate's ability to design a concrete mechanism that works correctly under contention while maintaining precise timing guarantees.

## Key Concepts

